      "content": "but it isnt just about being perfect. its like, i look at them and i see all the opportunities they're missing because of me. every day i'm around is just another day i'm failing them. it feels so selfish to keep holding onto them when i'm clearly just making their lives harder. wouldn't it be more compassionate to just let them start fresh, without all this baggage?",
